trans-unit.source: The type of an element in the controlled sequence.
trans-unit.target: 受控制序列中項目的類型。

trans-unit.source: The type of the underlying container.
trans-unit.target: 基礎容器的類型。

trans-unit.source: Defines the interface for an STL/CLR [queue](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/9ea7dec3-ea98-48ff-87d0-a5afc924aaf2) object.
trans-unit.target: 定義 STL/CLR [queue](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/9ea7dec3-ea98-48ff-87d0-a5afc924aaf2) 物件的介面。

trans-unit.source: The container adapter whose elements will be inserted into the container.
trans-unit.target: 其項目將插入容器中的容器配接器。

trans-unit.source: Replaces all elements of the container with the contents of the provided container.
trans-unit.target: 以所提供之容器的內容取代容器的所有項目。

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [queue::assign (STL/CLR)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/5bec8a84-9561-43f7-ad7f-f845d0edef41).
trans-unit.target: 如需詳細資訊，請參閱[queue::assign (STL/CLR)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/5bec8a84-9561-43f7-ad7f-f845d0edef41)。

trans-unit.source: Accesses the last element of the container.
trans-unit.target: 存取容器的最後一個項目。

trans-unit.source: The last element of the controlled sequence, which must be non-empty.
trans-unit.target: 受控制序列的最後一個項目，此序列必須為非空白序列。

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [queue::back (STL/CLR)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/983a5c0f-0a2f-475f-932b-e7dec9eaffbb).
trans-unit.target: 如需詳細資訊，請參閱[queue:: back (STL/CLR)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/983a5c0f-0a2f-475f-932b-e7dec9eaffbb)。

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the container contains no elements.
trans-unit.target: 判斷容器是否不含項目。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the container contains no elements; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果容器內沒有項目則為 <see langword="true" />，否則為 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [queue::empty (STL/CLR)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/318ccff9-23eb-4045-8c12-d3ea89159e87).
trans-unit.target: 如需詳細資訊，請參閱[queue:: empty (STL/CLR)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/318ccff9-23eb-4045-8c12-d3ea89159e87)。

trans-unit.source: Accesses the first element of the container.
trans-unit.target: 存取容器的第一個項目。

trans-unit.source: The first element of the controlled sequence, which must be non-empty.
trans-unit.target: 受控制序列的第一個項目，此序列必須為非空白序列。

trans-unit.target: 如需詳細資訊，請參閱[queue:: front (STL/CLR)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/9d7bb95f-5896-42f7-86fa-004a7a65cc94)。

trans-unit.source: Removes the last element of the container.
trans-unit.target: 移除容器的最後一個項目。

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [queue::pop (STL/CLR)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/38f6c03b-e8f8-4663-b3d6-18314cdc8e7d).

trans-unit.source: The value to add to the beginning of the container.
trans-unit.target: 要新增至容器開頭的值。

trans-unit.source: Adds an element to the beginning of the container.
trans-unit.target: 將項目新增至容器的開頭。

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [queue::push (STL/CLR)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/97cf1f98-d4c4-417f-b57a-89cdd351ef65).

trans-unit.source: Counts the number of elements in the container.
trans-unit.target: 計算容器中的項目數目。

trans-unit.source: The length of the controlled sequence.
trans-unit.target: 受控制序列的長度。
